section.section:
Within 3 business days of receipt of a tenant's written request under paragraph (1) of this subsection, an owner may provide to the tenant:
A current and valid risk reduction certificate;
A lead-free certificate;
A statement of verification by the owner and tenant of work performed in accordance with § 6-819(g) of the Environment Article for the affected property; or
The final report of an inspector verifying that work was performed on the affected property in accordance with § 6-819(g) of the Environment Article.
